Output docs/demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 12
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "./doikit cite --format chicago 10.1007/978-3-032-02801-3_5"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Sleep 1.5s

Type "./doikit check --file demo/dois.txt"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 25s

Sleep 2s
